  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DEBIE ZONE 2</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fun & challenging action adventure platformer with Ledge Climbing, Narrow Passages, Grappling Hook, Free Falling, Compass, Parachute, Ziplines, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Camera Switching System: 3rd person/1st Person</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sprint to cover vast distances in the blink of an eye</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parachute safely from heights or reach inaccessible areas</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into underwater worlds with swimming mechanics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swing through the skies using a versatile grappling hook</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with switches, push objects, and ride moving platforms to solve puzzles and explore new horizons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action Adventure style challenges, traps, puzzles, etc</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Double Jump</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grappling Hook</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slidable Slopes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sprint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crouch</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evade</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dash</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vault</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vine Wall Climb</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ledge Climb</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Narrow Passages</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swim</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zipline</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parachute</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ladder Climb</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push Objects</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Doors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compass</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traps, Obstacles, and Moving Platforms</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >... and more!</p>",
